  "gwSpecs": {
    "description": "Traditional boundaries have always existed between indoor and IP-rated outdoor fixtures.\nIP-rated fixtures were always heavier and bulkier, often featuring less output. They were\ndistinctly different.\nNow, with game-changing technologies and a new, totally innovative approach, the IP65-\nrated iFORTE® Fresnel negates the traditional weight penalty associated with IP-rated fixtures,\nhaving similar weight to the indoor FORTE®.\nWith class-leading form factor, size and appearance, and substitution of barndoors to a PLANO4™ four plane shutter module for\ngreater flexibility, iFORTE® Fresnel offers a perfect partner for the iFORTE®\nThe ingenious ingress protection system has been specifically designed to allow standard maintenance and preparation procedures\nto reduce workshop time.\nThe new iSE-TE™ 1.000W XP (Xtra performance) IP65-rated White LED TRANSFERABLE ENGINE technology provides greater\noutput while maintaining IP integrity, again needing no additional tools, with engine transfer capable of being conducted on-site for\nquick turnaround. Engine choices provide task flexibility.",
